---
title: "getAllowlistedSelectors (WorkflowRouter)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_load: allowlistedSelectors = s_workflowInfos[workflowId].allowlistedSelectors[target].values()
    q_load --> q_cast: assembly cast bytes32[] to bytes4[]
    q_cast --> [*]: return selectors

    note right of q_cast
        INV-001: assembly cast bytes32[] to bytes4[] reuses same memory pointer, caller sees only lower 4 bytes per slot
        INV-002: if workflowId or target not allowlisted, returns empty array (no revert)
    end note
